readme:
Service Usage

The service is to allow CMAL to replicate PAL and DAL identityand document data to Future Traveller via the ESB. Only the data required for matching will be replicated. Data describing alert types, treatment, history, etc will nto be replicated.

Service Behaviour

SV601.1 CMAL will replicate in real time, one message per PAL/DAL and send to ESB
SV601.2 ESB will process and deliver data to Future Traveller
SV601.3 A response will be sent back to CMAL of outcome of replication
